description: Zutec Holding AB engages in the development and marketing of cloud-based SaaS solutions for the construction and facilities management services sector. The company is headquartered in Dublin, Dublin and currently employs 28 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2018-03-15. The Company’s main product is a Zutec Platform for project data and documentation. The customers include architects, engineers, contractors and project owners. The product is used throughout the whole cycle of construction - from planning stage to the operation and maintenance stage. The firm provides Zutec Platform on both desktop and mobile platforms. Zutec Holding AB conducts its operations mainly through the subsidiary Zutec Inc. (Ireland) Ltd. The Company’s primary markets include Ireland, the United Kingdom, Qatar, among others.
